T16TD4449E:384b-2: # // dus gsum rgyal bas ji ltar thugs chud pa'i //
T16TD4449E:384b-3: chos kyi rang bzhin rig pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
T16TD4449E:384b-4: ma thob thob phyir brtson par mi byed kyang //
T16TD4449E:384b-5: snying rje'i bye brag thabs kyi spyod pa'ang ston //
T16TD4449E:384b-6: ji ltar mkha' la 'ja' tshon rnam mang yang //
T16TD4449E:384b-7: nam mkha'i ngang du ro gcig bye brag med //
T16TD4449E:384b-8: de bzhin rgyal ba'i gzugs sku rnam mang yang //
T16TD4449E:385a-1: su ro gcig bye brag med //
T16TD4449E:385a-2: bde gshegs snying po sems kyi rang bzhin la //
T16TD4449E:385a-3: yun ring dus nas rmongs pa'i sems can rnams //
T16TD4449E:385a-4: bdag tu 'dzin pa'i sems rgyud so sor snang //
T16TD4449E:385a-5: rang bzhin nyid ni rgyal ba'i chos skur gcig / ye shes sgyu mar snang ba'i sangs rgyas dang //
T16TD4449E:385a-6: log rtog sgyu mar snang ba'i sems can gnyis //
T16TD4449E:385a-7: ye shes log rtog khyad par bsam yas kyang //
T16TD4449E:385a-8: sgyu ma yin phyir rang bzhin yongs kyis mnyam //
T16TD4449E:385a-9: sems can sangs rgyas bden par tshul gcig cing //
T16TD4449E:385a-10: rang gi sems nyid sangs rgyas yin shes na //
T16TD4449E:385a-11: gzhan nas bsgrub par bya ba ci yang med //
T16TD4449E:385a-12: de lta bas na spang bar bya ba'ang med //
T16TD4449E:385a-13: 'di lta bu yi chos kyi tshul rig na //
T16TD4449E:385a-14: ma rig rnams la snying rje yongs kyis skye //
T16TD4449E:385a-15: snying rje skyes nas sgyu ma'i ting 'dzin gyis //
T16TD4449E:385a-16: phan 'dogs thabs kyi spyod pa cir yang ston //
T16TD4449E:385a-17: sangs rgyas dgongs pa ji lta ba //
T16TD4449E:385a-18: sems kyi rang bzhin gnas med de ltar bsgom //
T16TD4449E:385a-19: thugs rje'i 'bad pa rab 'byams ji lta ba //
T16TD4449E:385a-20: rnal 'byor thabs kyi ting 'dzin de ltar sprul //
T16TD4449E:385a-21: bdag dang bdag gir 'dzin pa med pa'i phyir //
T16TD4449E:385a-22: pha rol phyin drug dmigs med rdzogs par ldan //
T16TD4449E:385a-23: thabs kyi spyod pas gdul bya kun 'dul yang //
T16TD4449E:385a-24: sgyu ma'i blo ldan rlom sems ci yang med //
T16TD4449E:385a-25: ma skyes sems la sems can med pa'i phyir //
T16TD4449E:385a-26: ngo bo nyid kyi chos sku'i nga rgyal 'chang //
T16TD4449E:385a-27: chos kun sgyu mar mngon sum gsal ba'i phyir //
T16TD4449E:385a-28: ting 'dzin sgyu mas ci 'dus de ltar ston //
T16TD4449E:385a-29: chos sku mnyam nyid rtogs nas 'gro don du //
T16TD4449E:385a-30: bde gshegs byin rlabs cir yang ston pa ltar //
T16TD4449E:385a-31: bdag nyid chos sku rig pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
T16TD4449E:385a-32: thabs kyi bye brag da nas de ltar brjod //
T16TD4449E:385a-33: thabs dang shes rab ldan pa'i sgron ma rdzogs so /
T16TD4449E:385a-35: // / slob dpon dpal dbyangs kyis mdzad pa'o /
